General.Name: United Overseas Insurance Limited
General.Description: United Overseas Insurance Limited engages in the underwriting general insurance business in Singapore, ASEAN countries, and internationally. The company provides personal insurance products, including travel, accident protection, home, domestic helper, and motor insurance products. It also offers commercial general insurance products, such as fire, business interruption, machinery/equipment all risks, burglary and theft, money, marine cargo, fidelity guarantee, plate glass, public liability, work injury compensation, and group personal accident insurance products. In addition, the company offers directors' and officers' insurance; contractors' all risks/erection all risks insurance; and Takaful, an Islamic financial assurance to address misfortunes, accidents, or disasters. Further, it provides reinsurance products. The company was incorporated in 1971 and is headquartered in Singapore. United Overseas Insurance Limited is a subsidiary of United Overseas Bank Limited.
